─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
ANALYSIS
This bill modifies the facility in which alleged delinquent minors may be held in detention
pending an adjudicatory hearing, permitting alleged delinquent minors to be housed in a county
correctionsfacilityoncereachingage18.
